Author: OkieNope
Text: Always :/ I look for heights of models and cosplayers and think to myself "there's no excuse I can't look like her" funnily enough, most of them are actually at a much healthier / average weight than I am :/ it's kinda motivational for recovery purposes,  yet here I  am, still afraid to gain just a few to get into tripples oof

Author: loafloafloafloaf
Text: models: have won the genetic lottery, dedicate a lot of time into maintaining their physique, have a nutritionist and personal trainer, a good chance that they have disordered eating.  me: why can't i be that.
